name: The Best BBQ Dry Rub Recipe - @FoodNFTs
description: I'm a semi-professional chef and foodie. This is the PERFECT dry rub recipe for beef, pork or chicken. You can use a smoker, grill or frying pan! Here's the recipe: 1 cup Dark brown sugar 1/2 cup paprika 2 1/2 tbsp course black pepper 1 1/2 tsp chili powder 1 1/2 tbsp garlic powder 1 1/2 tbsp onion powder 1 tsp cayenne pepper 2 tbsp kosher salt
